{"tid":1268730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 71升旗禮站出來咆哮吧","createTime":"2019-06-30T11:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T22:02:30.000Z","uid":137502,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"857347d98014509b32ec96e63a05a85b9cc58889","tid":1268730,"uid":137502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"此時不爆發更待何時 今日我地所受嘅屈辱要十倍奉還 唔單止呀 係自從97回歸我地從來未抬起頭做人 聽日朝早我地香港人要第一次堂堂正正站出來同依個極權政府搏鬥 以死相搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地過往一個月嘅民主運動就係太多包伏 太多底線限制我地香港人 所以到現時我地香港人一樣訴求都爭取唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴力 無錯無人想發生 但再靠聽日晏就遊行等和平理性非暴力的民主運動 已經再唔能夠撼動港共政權 所以以武制暴係我地香港人唯一嘅出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽朝全體香港人一齊入金紫荊廣場睇升旗禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日睇升旗禮詳情如下 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1265427/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1265427/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/869zqWj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F869zqWj.jpg&h=b133a420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n9PLxBk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn9PLxBk.jpg&h=ea460a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHicW20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHicW20.jpg&h=9f9d6f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHLF5Wm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHLF5Wm.jpg&h=b56a8